summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements over portions of Tract 7, Merrick's Acre Tracts; and portions of Blocks 1 and 2, Elwood Addition for sanitary sewer purposes (55th Avenue South, et al, Sanitary Sewer); and over a portion of the Northeast one-quarter of Section 29, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., and of Lot 3, Wessley Park Addition for storm drain purposes.
